  m_text: 'Collect as many parcels as possible without getting caught by annoying
    old self-announced justice bringers.

    You delivered parcels once... NOW it''s
    time to regain what''s yours!


    If you get chased by old people, run behind
    buildings to cut their view! But be carefull! Old people have nothing to do,
    which means they remember you!


    When you get caught, you have a last chance
    to escape (a QTE).


    Each carried parcel slows you down. If you are happy
    with the outcome, get back to your truck and exfiltrate.


    Have Fun!'
